Description: Twilio allows you to integrate voice and SMS communications into your applications.
Name: Twilio SMS

Methods.Name: List Incoming Phone Numbers
Methods.Description: Return a list of all incoming phone numbers

Methods.Name: Update Incoming Phone Number
Methods.Description: Update the selected incoming phone number.

Methods.Name: Send SMS
Methods.Description: Send an SMS or MMS message. You must provide at least one of the following parameters - Message and Media URL - but both can be used.

Methods.Name: Retrieve SMS
Methods.Description: Get a single message by providing its MessageSid.

Methods.Name: Retrieve Messages List
Methods.Description: Get a list of messages associated with your account.

Methods.Name: Receive SMS
Methods.Description: Triggered when an SMS is sent to a number in your Twilio account

Methods.Name: List Accounts
Methods.Description: Retrieve a list of the Account resources belonging to the account used to make the API request. This list will include that Account as well.

MetaTile: Twilio SMS Integration | Marketing Automation | Cyclr
MetaDescription: Integrate Twilio's advance call & SMS platform into your sales & marketing plans by creating your own automation workflows with Cyclr's integration builder.
Content:
Turbocharge your sales and marketing communications by integrating Twilio’s powerful SMS platform.

Cyclr’s easy to use, drag & drop automation workflow builder allows you to connect Twilio to your application, providing quick installing automation workflows to your users.
